        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES. 15–25. Pantomorus albosignatus species group. Figs. 15-20 female terminalia. 15, Sternite VIII; 16, ovipositor; 17, P. albosignatus, spermatheca; 18, P. parvulus, spermatheca; 19, P. andersoni, spermatheca; 20, P. crinitus, spermatheca. Scales: 0.25 mm. Figs. 21-25 male genitalia. 21, P. albosignatus, penis, lateral view; 22, P. parvulus, penis, lateral view; 23, P. andersoni, penis, lateral view; 24, P. crinitus, penis, lateral view; 25, P. andersoni, dorsal view of apex. Figures 15–16, 21–25 scales= 0.50 mm. Figures 17–20 scales= 0.25 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4397150/files/figure.png" .

